Thanks all!  Your comments and encouragement fueled a productive discussion
to shape a candidate visioning process.

In our meeting we found agreement around:
- the SPARC question 5 should be a key input (if and whenever SPARC team
deems that data is available for release to COM in some form)
- we can design a service (tentatively Oct.18) to get congregation-wide
input
- a smaller group can develop candidate statements based on these inputs
- we can present the candidate statements for feedback and revision (at
least one round)
- we could have a vision statement ready for a vote by year end

Welcome any thoughts or reservations about this candidate process!

Kind regards,
Alex

